00:45:59.430 --> 00:46:01.130 align:middle line:90%
Gates, you're just delightful.

00:46:01.130 --> 00:46:03.050 align:middle line:84%
I just-- I love
what you've done.

00:46:03.050 --> 00:46:04.990 align:middle line:84%
