00:46:15.130 --> 00:46:17.020 align:middle line:84%
Now we have to put our
boots to the ground.

00:46:17.020 --> 00:46:18.320 align:middle line:90%
>>MCKIBBIN: I agree.

00:46:18.320 --> 00:46:20.782 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: So again, it was
